msgstr "Token para cron externo"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1232
msgid ""
"Technical options. The defaults work fine for most sites — only touch these "
"if you need to fine-tune behavior or you are diagnosing a problem."
msgstr ""
"Opcións técnicas. Os valores por defecto funcionan ben na maioría de sitios "
"— só as toques se precisas axustar o comportamento ou estás diagnosticando "
"un problema."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1364
msgid "Connection OK:"
msgstr "Conexión OK:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1369
msgid "Connection error:"
msgstr "Erro de conexión:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1419
msgid ""
"Saving automatically verifies the connection and permissions (does not alter "
"your DNS cache)."
msgstr ""
"Ao gardar verifícase automaticamente a conexión e os permisos (non altera a "
"túa caché de DNS)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1429
msgid "Console:"
msgstr "Consola:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1430
msgid "⏳ Wait a few seconds for the operation to complete…"
msgstr "⏳ Agarda uns segundos para que se complete a operación…"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1454
msgid "Active"
msgstr "Activo"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1454
msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Desactivado"

#. translators: %d is the number of days for log retention.
#: es-football-bypass.php:1456
#, php-format
msgid "Retention: %d days."
msgstr "Retención: %d días."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1458
msgid "Logging is disabled. Enable it in the Settings tab."
msgstr "O rexistro está desactivado. Actívao na lapela de Configuración."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1462
msgid "No events recorded yet."
msgstr "Aínda non hai eventos rexistrados."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1464
msgid "The log file exists but contains no recent events."
msgstr "O ficheiro de log existe pero non contén eventos recentes."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1469
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Data"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1469
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipo"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1469
msgid "Message"
msgstr "Mensaxe"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1469
msgid "Context"
msgstr "Contexto"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1483
msgid "Showing the 250 most recent events."
msgstr "Móstranse os 250 eventos máis recentes."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1498
msgid ""
"Global API Key requires email. User tokens are in My Profile. Account tokens "
"are in Manage Account > Account API Tokens (requires Super Administrator). "
"Minimum permissions: Zone:Read, DNS:Read, DNS:Edit."
msgstr ""
"Global API Key require email. Os tokens de usuario están en O Meu Perfil. Os "
"tokens de conta están en Xestionar conta > Account API Tokens (require Super "
"Administrator). Permisos mínimos: Zone:Read, DNS:Read, DNS:Edit."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1515
msgid "Never shown in traces or console."
msgstr "Nunca se mostra en trazas nin na consola."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1530
msgid ""
"Required only for account tokens. You can find it in the URL of the "
"Cloudflare dashboard: dash.cloudflare.com/ACCOUNT_ID"
msgstr ""
"Obrigatorio só para tokens de conta. Atoparalo no URL do panel de "
"Cloudflare: dash.cloudflare.com/ACCOUNT_ID"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1537
msgid "Could not be detected"
msgstr "Non se puido detectar"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1538
msgid ""
"The server outgoing IP could not be determined. Verify that the server has "
"Internet access."
msgstr ""
"Non se puido determinar a IP de saída do servidor. Comproba que o servidor "
"ten acceso a Internet."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1541
msgid ""
"This is the IP your server uses to communicate with the Cloudflare API. You "
"can restrict your API Token to this IP for added security."
msgstr ""
"Esta é a IP que o teu servidor usa para comunicarse coa API de Cloudflare. "
"Podes restrinxir o teu API Token a esta IP para máis seguridade."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1549
msgid ""
"Multiple outgoing IPs have been detected. Your server may use any of them to "
"communicate with the Cloudflare API. Add all of them when restricting your "
"API Token."
msgstr ""
"Detectáronse varias IPs de saída. O teu servidor pode usar calquera delas "
"para comunicarse coa API de Cloudflare. Engade todas ao restrinxir o teu API "
"Token."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1563
msgid ""
"Select the records to manage in the <strong>Operation</strong> tab (using "
"the cache)."
msgstr ""
"Marca os rexistros a xestionar na lapela <strong>Operación</strong> (usando "
"a caché)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1574
msgid ""
"Minutes that must pass after disabling Cloudflare before checking if it can "
"be reactivated (5-1440)."
msgstr ""
"Minutos que deben pasar tras desactivar Cloudflare antes de volver comprobar "
"se pode reactivarse (5-1440)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1586
msgid ""
"Ignore \"blocked\" states whose most recent stateChange in hayahora.futbol "
"is older than this (1-72 hours, default 6). Prevents orphan records from "
"keeping the bypass active indefinitely when a close event was never "
"published."
msgstr ""
"Ignora os estados «bloqueado» cuxo stateChange máis recente en "
"hayahora.futbol sexa anterior a este prazo (1-72 horas, por defecto 6). "
"Evita que rexistros orfos manteñan o bypass activo indefinidamente cando "
"nunca se publicou o evento de peche."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1594
msgid "Simple (recommended for clients)"
msgstr "Simple (recomendado para clientes)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1595
msgid "Advanced (show diagnostics, logs, cron settings and technical details)"
msgstr ""
"Avanzado (mostrar diagnóstico, logs, configuración do cron e detalles "
"técnicos)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1596
msgid ""
"Simple mode hides the feed diagnostics panel, the logs tab, the technical "
"console and the advanced options (staleness threshold, log retention and "
"external cron token) — leaving only the block status, the manual proxy ON/"
"OFF buttons and the basic email notifications. Logs are still written to "
"disk: switch to Advanced temporarily if you need to diagnose a problem or "
"configure an external cron."
msgstr ""
"O modo simple agocha o panel de diagnóstico do feed, a pestana de logs, a "
"consola técnica e as opcións avanzadas (limiar de obsolescencia, retención "
"de logs e token de cron externo), deixando só o estado de bloqueo, os botóns "
"manuais de proxy ON/OFF e os avisos por correo básicos. Os logs séguense "
"escribindo no disco: cambia a Avanzado temporalmente se precisas "
"diagnosticar un problema ou configurar un cron externo."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1604
msgid "Send an email when the bypass turns on or off automatically"
msgstr "Enviar un correo cando o bypass se active ou desactive automaticamente"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1605
msgid ""
"Emails are sent only on actual state changes from the cron (not on manual "
"override). A 2-minute throttle prevents bursts if the feed oscillates."
msgstr ""
"Os correos envíanse só cando hai un cambio real de estado polo cron (non en "
"forzado manual). Un throttle de 2 minutos evita refachos se o feed oscila."

#. translators: %s is the site administrator email address.
#: es-football-bypass.php:1620
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Optional. Leave empty to use the site administrator address (%s). Set a "
"different address here to send notifications elsewhere — useful when the "
"plugin is managed by an agency or support team and the site admin is the "
"final client."
msgstr ""
"Opcional. Déixao baleiro para usar o enderezo do administrador do sitio "
"(%s). Pon outro enderezo aquí para que os avisos cheguen a un destinatario "
"diferente — útil cando o plugin o xestiona unha axencia ou un equipo de "
"soporte e o admin do sitio é o cliente final."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1632
msgid ""
"Minimum number of distinct ISPs (providers) with currently blocked IPs "
"needed to consider there is a real mass block (1-20, default 2). Lower "
"values are more sensitive; 1 triggers on any single-ISP glitch. Only applies "
"when the feed publishes ISP information; ignored otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Número mínimo de provedores (ISPs) distintos con IPs actualmente bloqueadas "
"necesarios para considerar que hai un bloqueo masivo real (1-20, por defecto "
"2). Valores baixos son máis sensibles; 1 dispara ante o fallo dun só ISP. Só "
"se aplica cando o feed publica información por ISP; en caso contrario "
"ignórase."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1639
msgid ""
"Disable Proxy during football (General=YES), without waiting for this domain "
"detection"
msgstr ""
"Desactivar Proxy cando hai fútbol (Xeral=SI), sen agardar detección deste "
"dominio"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1640
msgid ""
"IMPORTANT: With this option enabled, the proxy will be automatically "
"disabled when hayahora.futbol indicates active blocks (General=YES), even if "
"your specific domain has not been detected as blocked."
msgstr ""
"IMPORTANTE: Con esta opción activada, o proxy desactivarase automaticamente "
"cando hayahora.futbol indique que hai bloqueos activos (Xeral=SI), aínda que "
"o teu dominio específico non fose detectado como bloqueado."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1641
msgid ""
"Useful to avoid false negatives when you know your site is blocked during "
"football events but IP detection doesn't always work correctly."
msgstr ""
"Útil para evitar falsos negativos cando sabes que o teu sitio é bloqueado "
"durante eventos de fútbol pero a detección de IP non sempre funciona "
"correctamente."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1648
msgid "Save actions to log (cron and manual)"
msgstr "Gardar accións no rexistro (cron e manuais)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1649
msgid ""
"Logs are stored in the uploads directory, protected with .htaccess, and "
"displayed in the Logs tab."
msgstr ""
"Os rexistros gárdanse no directorio uploads, protexidos con .htaccess, e "
"móstranse na lapela Logs."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1660
msgid "Number of days to keep logs (minimum 1)."
msgstr "Número de días a conservar rexistros (mínimo 1)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1675
msgid ""
"Optional. Use a real server cron when WP-Cron is unreliable (low-traffic "
"sites, hosts that disable it). Leave empty to disable the external endpoint."
msgstr ""
"Opcional. Usa un cron real do servidor cando WP-Cron non sexa fiable (sitios "
"con pouco tráfico, hostings que o desactivan). Déixao baleiro para "
"desactivar o endpoint externo."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1678
msgid "URL to request:"
msgstr "URL a consultar:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1682
msgid "Crontab example (server cron):"
msgstr "Exemplo de crontab (cron do servidor):"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1686
msgid "To regenerate the token, empty the field and save."
msgstr "Para rexenerar o token, baleira o campo e garda."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1693
msgid ""
"Delete all plugin data when this plugin is uninstalled from Plugins → "
"Installed Plugins → Delete"
msgstr ""
"Borrar todos os datos do plugin cando se desinstale desde Plugins → Plugins "
"instalados → Borrar"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1694
msgid ""
"Only applies at uninstall time, not when the plugin is deactivated. When "
"checked (default), uninstalling removes settings, Cloudflare credentials, "
"DNS cache and logs. Uncheck this if you plan to reinstall later and want to "
"keep the configuration. The scheduled cron and temporary caches are always "
"cleaned up regardless of this setting."
msgstr ""
"Só se aplica ao desinstalar, non ao desactivar. Se está marcado (por "
"defecto), ao desinstalar bórrase a configuración, as credenciais de "
"Cloudflare, a caché DNS e os logs. Desmárcao se pensas reinstalar despois e "
"queres conservar a configuración. O cron programado e as cachés temporais "
"lísanse sempre, independentemente deste axuste."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1716
msgid "YES"
msgstr "SI"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1716
msgid "NO"
msgstr "NON"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1719
msgid ""
"Right now there are active IP blocks linked to La Liga matches. Your site "
"may be affected."
msgstr ""
"Agora mesmo hai bloqueos de IP activos vinculados a partidos de La Liga. O "
"teu sitio pode estar afectado."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1720
msgid ""
"Right now no IP blocks linked to La Liga matches are detected. Everything "
"normal."
msgstr ""
"Agora mesmo non se detectan bloqueos de IP vinculados a partidos de La Liga. "
"Todo normal."

#. translators: %s is a date/time like "2026-04-17 22:03:45".
#: es-football-bypass.php:1729
#, php-format
msgid "Last update: %s"
msgstr "Última actualización: %s"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1731
msgid "Affected ISPs:"
msgstr "ISPs afectados:"

#: es-football-bypass.php:1736
msgid "Where this data comes from"
msgstr "De onde saen estes datos"

#. translators: %s is a link to hayahora.futbol.
#: es-football-bypass.php:1739
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The answer above comes from the public feed published by %s, which monitors "
"IP blocks ordered during La Liga football matches in Spain from several "
"Spanish ISPs (DIGI, Movistar, Orange, Masmovil…)."
msgstr ""
"A resposta de enriba vén do feed público publicado por %s, que monitoriza os "
"bloqueos de IPs ordenados durante partidos de fútbol de La Liga en España "
"desde varios ISPs españois (DIGI, Movistar, Orange, Masmovil…)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1742
msgid ""
"The feed URL is https://hayahora.futbol/estado/data.json and is consulted "
"automatically each time this page is opened."
msgstr ""
"A URL do feed é https://hayahora.futbol/estado/data.json e consúltase "
"automaticamente cada vez que se abre esta páxina."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1763
msgid "Local environment detected"
msgstr "Contorno local detectado"

#. translators: %s is the detected domain
#: es-football-bypass.php:1766
#, php-format
msgid ""
"The current domain is %s, which corresponds to a local environment or an IP "
"address. This plugin needs a public domain accessible from the Internet to "
"work correctly (DNS resolution, Cloudflare API and block checking)."
msgstr ""
"O dominio actual é %s, que corresponde a un contorno local ou a un enderezo "
"IP. Este plugin necesita un dominio público accesible desde Internet para "
"funcionar correctamente (resolución DNS, API de Cloudflare e comprobación de "
"bloqueos)."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1769
msgid ""
"Install the plugin on your production or staging site with a real domain to "
"use it."
msgstr ""
"Instala o plugin no teu sitio de produción ou staging cun dominio real para "
"usalo."

#: es-football-bypass.php:1771
msgid "Go to Settings"
msgstr "Ir a Configuración"

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3238
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] Cloudflare proxy disabled due to football blocks"
msgstr "[%s] Proxy de Cloudflare desactivado por bloqueos do fútbol"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3239
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"Active IP blocks from La Liga have been detected and the Cloudflare proxy "
"has been automatically disabled on the configured DNS records."
msgstr ""
"Ola,\n"
"\n"
"Detectáronse bloqueos de IP activos por parte de La Liga e o proxy de "
"Cloudflare desactivouse automaticamente nos rexistros DNS configurados."

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3240 es-football-bypass.php:3254
#, php-format
msgid "Site: %s"
msgstr "Sitio: %s"

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3241 es-football-bypass.php:3255
#, php-format
msgid "URL: %s"
msgstr "URL: %s"

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3242
msgid "State: Proxy OFF (DNS Only)"
msgstr "Estado: Proxy OFF (DNS Only)"

#. translators: %s is the internal reason code.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3244
#, php-format
msgid "Reason: %s"
msgstr "Motivo: %s"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3246
msgid ""
"The selected DNS records have switched from Proxied (CDN) to DNS Only so "
"your site remains reachable during the blocks."
msgstr ""
"Os rexistros DNS seleccionados pasaron de Proxied (CDN) a DNS Only para que "
"o teu sitio continúe sendo accesible durante os bloqueos."

#: es-football-bypass.php:3247
msgid ""
"The proxy will be re-enabled automatically once the blocks end and the "
"configured cooldown passes."
msgstr ""
"O proxy reactivarase automaticamente cando rematen os bloqueos e pase o "
"período de espera configurado."

#. translators: %s is the plugin Operation page URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3248 es-football-bypass.php:3258
#, php-format
msgid "Current status: %s"
msgstr "Estado actual: %s"

#. translators: %s is the plugin version.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3249 es-football-bypass.php:3259
#, php-format
msgid "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare v%s"
msgstr "ES Football Bypass for Cloudflare v%s"

#. translators: %s is the site name.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3252
#, php-format
msgid "[%s] Cloudflare proxy re-enabled"
msgstr "[%s] Proxy de Cloudflare reactivado"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3253
msgid ""
"Hello,\n"
"\n"
"No active La Liga IP blocks are detected. The Cloudflare proxy has been re-"
"enabled automatically."
msgstr ""
"Ola,\n"
"\n"
"Non se detectan bloqueos de IP activos de La Liga. O proxy de Cloudflare "
"reactivouse automaticamente."

#. translators: %s is the site URL.
#: es-football-bypass.php:3256
msgid "State: Proxy ON (CDN)"
msgstr "Estado: Proxy ON (CDN)"

#: es-football-bypass.php:3257
msgid ""
"The selected DNS records are back on Proxied (CDN). Normal operation resumed."
msgstr ""
"Os rexistros DNS seleccionados volveron a Proxied (CDN). Funcionamento "
"normal restablecido."

